# 🚀 Weiyang Open Lab

Welcome to **Weiyang Open Lab** 👋

We are a research-driven team focused on building intelligent systems at the intersection of **AI, robotics, and data science**.

---

## 🔬 Research Areas

* 🤖 **Robotics**
  Autonomous systems, control, and embodied intelligence

* ⏳ **Time Series Modeling**
  Forecasting, anomaly detection, and financial modeling

* 🧠 **Machine Learning & AI**
  Deep learning, representation learning, and model interpretability

* 📊 **Quantitative Finance**
  Data-driven trading strategies and market modeling

* 🧩 **Explainable AI (XAI)**
  Interpretable models and decision transparency

---

